title: That’s bad for all of us.

author: Russell Brand
description:
A US airstrike on Iranian nuclear facilities, a flood of coordinated Western media posts, and now regime change rhetoric from Trump—are we watching history repeat itself? One news report even compares it to the plot of Top Gun: Maverick, as if this is all just entertainment. But this isn’t a movie—people are dying. I break down how legacy media, political elites, and globalist interests might be driving us into yet another endless war. Let’s question the narrative before it’s too late.
